readme 
=========
Previous drivers are not included!

This driver is for the final milestone.

To compile the driver, type
	make 

To run the driver, type 'test.out' followed by the query # you wish to execute
	./test.out [0-3]

When you successfully complete the codebase, 
the output of test.out should include 
	the input SQL query, 
	the query plan tree, 
	the pipe information (i.e., the pipe ID and its memory address),
	the query execution order (operator by operator), 
	and the returning results.  

Note:
	In this codebase, the configuration of data paths is in QueryOptimizer.cc instead of test.h or test.cat. 
	In QueryOptimizer.cc, you need to update the `tpch_dir` to the data/10M/ path and the `dbfile_dir` to the data/bin/ path of your system, 
	just like what you did in previous milestones.  
